data.description: Enjoy total privacy and comfort in this superb single-family home! Nestled in an inviting neighborhood, this residence offers an unparalleled living experience designed for those who appreciate style and convenience. This property has three bedrooms.     There are lots of updates. New updates have been made to the heating and cooling unit and more. Additionally, step outside to your private haven, a beautifully landscaped yard and park that serves as your personal retreat. Whether it's hosting summer barbecues on the patio, watching your kids play on the lawn, or simply enjoying a quiet evening. This outdoor space adds a whole new dimension to your living experience.
